folder: Division Street & Market Street, Manhattan, NY
text:
(1) Division Street, west from but not including Market Street. The view is taken from the Manhattan Bridge.

September 24, 1927.

P. L. Sperr.

(2) The same, at a later date, showing the skeleton of the U.S. Court House in the background.

March 9, 1934.

P. L. Sperr.
